	   <tr><td colspan=2>make hotkeys for your fav/most useful songs. then use the keypad to twist. first start song 1 and either wait till you see the icon or the mssg for the song. then stop that song by hitting any number for the hotkey bank and start song 2. do the same thing and you can twist 3-4 songs. you'll eventually get good enuff to switch in instruments/weapons and even stop a song and start another b4 it gives the mssg/icon but you time it just right so it still appears (kinda hard to xplain there - try it yourself)&nbsp;&nbsp; =D<br><br><br>Taamas Starsinger<br>52nd Minstrel of Saryrn<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
