	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hell levels are 30, 35, 40, 45, 50 and anything over 50. The algorithm at these levels is tweaked, and you need alot more experience points to level through these.<br>Uber is German for super, I think. Anyway, it generally refers to the statistically better, more difficult to obtain items in the game. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
